# Module

## Uses

::READ (Construct: NaturalExpression) FROM `../expressions/natural-expression.art`.
::READ (Construct: NaturalExpression) FROM `../expressions/natural-name.art`.

## Construct: FieldInline

**Category:** Inline

**Purpose:** Represent a named property value expressed on a single line.

**Description:** A FieldInline associates a name with an inline value within a SectionBlock. The value is a NaturalExpression defined on the same line as the field name.

**Schema:**

```art
FieldInline {
    name: <NaturalName>
    value: <NaturalExpression>
}
```

**Syntax:**

```art
<FieldInline> =
	**<NaturalName (field.name)>:** <NaturalExpression>
```

**Rules:**

- A FieldInline MUST define a name.
- A FieldInline MUST define a value on the same line as the name.
- A FieldInline value MUST be a NaturalExpression.

**Example:**

```md
**Status:** IN-PROGRESS
```
